author: PlayStation
description:
Mika and the Witch's Mountain release on January 2nd 
Mika and the Witch’s Mountain is a fantasy adventure about an aspiring witch who delivers packages to the townspeople of a small island. Explore every cranny and soar through the sky with your magic broom.

- Fly over a beautiful island. Explore a mini open world full of secrets and magic.
- Protect the packages from the elements as you fly around the island.
- Play as a little witch who works delivering packages on a small island.
- Complete your collection with outfits, trails, treasures, and more.
- A cozy light-heart story for you to unwind and relax.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
title: Mika and the Witch's Mountain - Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
